		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />GB Kid Icarus (a sequel, in fact) is not more similar to the NES game than games like Duck Tales or Mega Man. I.e. it is similar in design and gameplay, reuses the same graphics, but has many differences, like less levels, different level maps, etc. Kid Icarus has the maze levels that aren't present in NES version.

		

